# AllenGreen Transportation — Website Delivery Report

**Prepared for:** AllenGreen Group LLC
**Delivered by:** [Your Agency Name]
**Delivery Date:** March 4, 2026
**Live Website:** [allengreentransportation.com](https://allengreentransportation.com)

---

## Project Overview

AllenGreen Transportation engaged us to fully redesign and rebuild their digital presence. The previous website was hosted on Wix, which was limited in functionality, performance, and scalability. We transferred the domain from Wix to **Lytehosting**, rebuilt the website from the ground up as a **custom, full-stack web application**, and deployed it to production.

The result is a premium, high-performance transportation platform — not just a brochure website — complete with booking management, a client portal, a corporate accounts system, real-time shipment tracking, a blog, an AI-powered live chat assistant, and a full back-office admin dashboard.

---

## Technology Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| **Frontend Framework** | React 18 + TypeScript |
| **Routing** | React Router v6 (Single Page Application) |
| **Styling** | Tailwind CSS + Radix UI components |
| **Database** | Supabase (PostgreSQL) — cloud-hosted |
| **Authentication** | Supabase Auth (JWT-based, secure) |
| **Email System** | Resend (via Supabase Edge Functions) |
| **AI Chat** | Custom AI assistant with company knowledge base |
| **Hosting** | Lytehosting cPanel (Apache) |
| **Domain** | allengreentransportation.com (transferred from Wix) |
| **Email Verification** | DKIM + SPF DNS records (fully verified) |

