## Key Features Built

### 📬 Automated Email System
Powered by **Resend** with the verified sender `bookings@allengreentransportation.com`:
- **New quote submitted** → automatic confirmation email sent to client + alert sent to admin
- **Quote status updated** (price quoted by admin) → email with quoted price sent to client
- **Trip completed** → review request email sent to client with Google Review link

### 🤖 AI Chat Assistant ("Allen")
- Live chat widget present on every page
- Powered by a custom knowledge base built around AllenGreen's services, pricing, fleet, and FAQs
- Answers client questions instantly without requiring a phone call

### 📍 Real-Time Booking Tracker
- Clients can track their ride or freight shipment at `/track` using their booking reference
- Admin can update tracking events (Received → Picked Up → In Transit → Out for Delivery → Delivered)

### 💬 Blog with Comments
- 4 article categories: Airport, Corporate, Medical, Freight
- Full tagging system with tag filters
- Comments section on each article (comments require admin approval before going live)
- Related articles and recent posts sidebar

### 🌐 Multi-Language Support
- Global language toggle in the header
- Supports English, Spanish, French, and more

### 🍪 Cookie Consent Banner
- GDPR-compliant cookie notice on first visit

### 📝 Careers / Job Applications
- Job listings managed in admin dashboard
- Online application form (with consent checkbox)
- Admin receives and manages all applications in the back-office

### 📱 Fully Mobile Responsive
- All pages are optimised for mobile, tablet, and desktop
- Touch-friendly navigation and buttons throughout

### 🔒 Security
- All database tables protected by Row Level Security (RLS) via Supabase
- Admin area protected behind authentication — not guessable by URL alone
- DKIM + SPF email authentication fully verified (no spoofing, delivery to inbox)
- API keys stored as server-side secrets — never exposed to the browser

---

## Database & Infrastructure

The website uses a **live cloud database** (Supabase / PostgreSQL) with the following data tables:

| Table | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `quotes` | All booking/quote requests |
| `tracking_events` | Ride and shipment tracking updates |
| `corporate_accounts` | Business client accounts |
| `job_applications` | Career applications |
| `contact_messages` | Contact form submissions |
| `job_listings` | Open positions (managed by admin) |
| `testimonials` | Client reviews (managed by admin) |
| `profiles` | Customer account profiles |
| `blog_comments` | Blog comment submissions (with moderation) |
| `chat_messages` | Live chat conversation logs |

