## Recommended Next Steps (Post-Launch)

1. **Test a live booking** — submit a quote at `/quote` and confirm you receive the email notification
2. **Approve the first admin account** — log in at `/ag-ops-hub/login` and familiarise yourself with the dashboard
3. **Add real testimonials** — in the Admin dashboard, add verified client reviews to display on the homepage
4. **Publish job listings** — if hiring, create listings in the Admin dashboard so they appear on the Careers page
5. **Add spam protection** (recommended 30–60 days post-launch) — add a CAPTCHA or honeypot to the contact and quote forms
6. **Google Search Console** — submit the sitemap to get indexed on Google

